item.title: Prayer bpn13046 in Kube
item.description: *Ic mêŋŋê ac hêla hocmac. imuac kewu nêŋ uŋa kicga aumac zêma gi kewu selia nec qesi mima niŋ selima hêmbipia iguc tacma qesi mina: O Nemu Yanda, Ni ewa qerina melemba geŋgamoru tilêŋtilêŋ kucgawac qeru haʒac geŋga moru sac hiwa haʒac waŋŋu geŋga kucyandaga qeriaguc hiwa haʒac. O Nemu, hia mindiŋŋina uŋanawac kiwa hiwa hayu geŋga asac gaŋŋê qerina wac kifaya ze asariyiu siŋi yomuaru uŋana niniŋ kuc hiabia memac.
